Description: fn-knock is a gateway and management panel for private service exposure
 fn-knock provides reverse proxy, authentication, SSL certificates,
 DDNS management, IP whitelist, WAF firewall, and tunnel integration
 (Cloudflared/frp) in a single panel. Designed for NAS and home servers.
